short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Gives Get Out the Rotten Tomatoes Score it Deserves

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This is your Chrome extension that replaces the Rotten Tomatoes score for Get Out with the one it deserves. Also prevents other perfect scores from being ruined by a single bad reviewer.
